    <briefdescription>
<para>Single key/value entry used by <ref refid="class_c_named_value_table" kindref="compound">CNamedValueTable</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The entry owns a copy of the key string. The value is stored directly and is intentionally public so callers can update it after a lookup without another wrapper function.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>TValue</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Type of the stored value. The value type must be copyable. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
